page.title: 09HOMELIFE: AT HOME
page.content: My name is Paul Smith age 12.When I arrived home at 3:55 I had some biscuits and watched TV.At 6:30 I had some tea and at 7:30 I started my homework.At 7:40 I had a 10 minute run ,I then resumed homework untill 8:45. At 9:00 I had my shower.At 9:20 I read my book and at 9:40 I brushed my teeth and went to bed. My name is Julie Blyth age 12.When I got home from school at 4:00 and started to do my homework.At 6:00 I had my chicken and chips for tea.At 7:00 I went roller skating which finished at 9:00.I came home and continued my homework.I had a bath at 9:30 and went to bed at 10:00.
